data.title: AMNESIA MOON. by Lethem, Jonathan: Signed by Author(s)
data.meta_description: Signed by Author(s) - 1st Edition - Hardcover - New York: Harcourt Brace & Company, (1995) dj - Dust Jacket Included - SIGNED hardcover first edition - First printing. His second book - called a wonderfully skewed road novel - Oz rewritten in a bleak future. "Since the war and the bombs, Hatfork, Wyoming is a sick town." SIGNED on the title page. 247 pp. Fine in fine dust jacket. - AMNESIA MOON.
